DBB
•   Reduces cost b planning everything early and avoid mistakes later
•   Gives architects full control earlier
•   Better for public sector due to competitive bidding
•   Takes longer
DB
•   DB no incentive for competitive price or varied proposal so it is more costly
•   Gives CM more control
•   All planners and GC have design input at start 
•   Easier to fast-track
Integrated Project Delivery (IPD) because the use of newer technologies allows for more communication/collaboration/teamwork. IPD generally emphasizes collaboration by having everyone involved early on. This involvement and tech like the 4D model help foresee possible risk – increased value opportunities and less waste from mistakes.

